						               													<description>A board game with bananas, party and a sleepy monkey.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The kongs are planning a party that lasted for 3 days and 3 nights but the alpha-kong, KONGKANG, who loves his beauty sleep, greatly disapproves. To get around this &amp;ldquo;Operation PARTY&amp;rdquo; is born. The quietest kong of each night will get bananas as a reward. But the noisiest kong will get a banana peel in the face instead. At the end of the third night, the party must end because by then KONGKANG will be wide awake. You must hoard as much banana as possible before KONGKANG wakes up. The kong that collects the most bananas wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Kongkang: the wild party is a party card game based on a traditional card game from Southern Thailand called &amp;quot;Kang&amp;quot;. Players try to get rid of high cards and keep the low one.  But that is not all, you can steal banana tokens from you another player via in-game Flow mechanic. Or use ability card to hinder other players. The player who has the lowest hand when the round end, wins banana tokens. After three rounds, the player with the most banana tokens wins the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
